data.description: Discover the charm of this 1,456 sqft, 3-bed, 2-bath home on 6.6 serene acres. Move in ready home waiting for your personal touch, this single-story gem offers two barns and multiple outbuildings, perfect for animals or hobbies. Enjoy vast open spaces, privacy, and breathtaking views. Conveniently located, yet a world apart, this property invites your vision to come to life. Create your ideal rural oasis – your dream country home awaits!
